asset.author: Nike
asset.hookText:
In preparation for our upcoming SB Chronicles Vol. 2 release, Nike SB pro Ishod Wair introduces a special "unplugged" version of Youness Amrani's part from SB Chronicles Vol. 1.

Nike SB's new full-length video The SB Chronicles Vol. 2 hits iTunes on December 10th.

Check out http://www.SBChronicles.com for more information.
